# ?ВҖ?ВҖ HTTP Server ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# TCP port the Express server listens on.
HTTP_PORT=3080

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ HTTPS / TLS ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# Set HTTPS_ENABLED=true to start the server over TLS (requires cert + key).
# HTTPS_PORT        : TLS listen port (default 3443; 443 requires root/CAP_NET_BIND_SERVICE)
# SSL_CERT_PATH     : Path to PEM certificate, relative to server/ directory
# SSL_KEY_PATH      : Path to PEM private key, relative to server/ directory
# SSL_CA_PATH       : (optional) CA / intermediate bundle, relative to server/ directory
# HTTP_REDIRECT     : Set true to keep plain HTTP on PORT and issue 301 -> HTTPS
HTTPS_ENABLED=true
HTTPS_PORT=3443
SSL_CERT_PATH=./certs/server.crt
SSL_KEY_PATH=./certs/server.key
# SSL_CA_PATH=./certs/ca.crt
HTTP_REDIRECT=true

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ Storage Backend ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# DB_TYPE=json    : Default ??all data stored in storage/lts.json (no external DB required).
# DB_TYPE=mongodb : Write-through to MongoDB; lts.json still written as warm-standby backup.
DB_TYPE=mongodb

# MongoDB connection URI (required only when DB_TYPE=mongodb).
# Format: mongodb://[user:pass@]host[:port]/dbname[?options]
# Atlas example: mongodb+srv://user:pass@cluster.mongodb.net/lts?retryWrites=true&w=majority
MONGODB_URI=json

# Override the database name extracted from MONGODB_URI.
# Useful when the URI points to a shared cluster and the DB name must be specified separately.
MONGODB_DB_NAME=lts

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ Server Environment ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# development : ONNX uses a single intra-op thread (light load, suitable for dev/test servers).
# production  : ONNX thread count = max(2, min(8, CPU_cores / 2)).
NODE_ENV=development

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ Runtime OS / Node binary selection ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# SERVER_RUNTIME_OS=auto     : Detect from current OS (win32 -> windows, else linux)
# SERVER_RUNTIME_OS=windows  : Force Windows mode
# SERVER_RUNTIME_OS=linux    : Force Linux mode
# NODE_EXEC                  : Explicit node executable to use on any OS (highest priority)
# NODE_EXEC_WINDOWS          : Node executable for Windows mode
# NODE_EXEC_LINUX            : Node executable for Linux mode
# PYTHON_EXEC                : Explicit python executable to use on any OS (highest priority)
# PYTHON_EXEC_WINDOWS        : Python executable for Windows mode
# PYTHON_EXEC_LINUX          : Python executable for Linux mode
# LTS_SKIP_PYTHON_EXPORT=1   : Skip optional Python-based ONNX export in OS scripts
SERVER_RUNTIME_OS=windows
NODE_EXEC=
NODE_EXEC_WINDOWS=C:\Program Files\nodejs\node.exe
NODE_EXEC_LINUX=/usr/bin/node
PYTHON_EXEC=
PYTHON_EXEC_WINDOWS=C:\Users\young.ho.kim\AppData\Local\Programs\Python\Python312\python.exe
PYTHON_EXEC_LINUX=/usr/bin/python3
LTS_SKIP_PYTHON_EXPORT=0

# в”Җв”Җ Server Mode в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
# combined  (default) вҖ” capture + AI inference + WebRTC + REST API in one process
# streaming           вҖ” capture + WebRTC only; forwards frames to ANALYSIS_SERVER_URL
# analysis            вҖ” AI inference only; exposes /api/analysis/frame; no camera capture
SERVER_MODE=analysis

# в”Җв”Җ Remote Analysis Server (used when SERVER_MODE=streaming) в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
# Base URL of the remote AI analysis server.
# Example: http://192.168.1.50:3001  or  https://ai.internal:3443
ANALYSIS_SERVER_URL=

# HTTP port used by the analysis server process (npm run analysis / dev:analysis)
ANALYSIS_HTTP_PORT=3443

# Timeout (ms) for each frame HTTP request. Frames exceeding this are dropped.
ANALYSIS_REQUEST_TIMEOUT_MS=2000

# Max in-flight concurrent analysis requests. Excess frames are dropped (back-pressure).
ANALYSIS_MAX_CONCURRENT=100

# powershell
# 1. кё°мЎҙ мәҗмӢң л°Ҹ мһҳлӘ» м„Өм№ҳлҗң нҸҙлҚ” м ңкұ°
# rm -Recurse -Force .\node_modules\, .\package-lock.json
# npm cache clean --force
# 
# 2. ONNX Runtime мҶҢмҠӨ л№Ңл“ң нҷҳкІҪ ліҖмҲҳлҘј нҷңм„ұнҷ”н•ң л’Ө м„Өм№ҳ
# $env:ONNXRUNTIME_NODE_BUILD_FROM_SOURCE="1"
# npm install onnxruntime-node
#
# Linux / macOS / WSL2 кё°мӨҖ
# bash
# rm -rf node_modules package-lock.json
# ONNXRUNTIME_NODE_BUILD_FROM_SOURCE=1 npm install onnxruntime-node

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ ONNX Runtime CUDA ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# Set to 1 to enable the CUDA execution provider (requires a CUDA-enabled onnxruntime-node build).
# When enabled: executionProviders=['cuda','cpu'], intraOpNumThreads=1 (GPU handles parallelism).
# Leave 0 (or omit) to use CPU-only inference.
ONNX_CUDA=0

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ ONNX intra-op thread count per mode ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# Number of CPU threads used per ONNX inference session.
# 0 = auto (production default: max(2, min(8, CPU_cores / 2))).
# Increase ONNX_THREADS_DEV/PROD for multi-core servers; keep low on edge devices.
ONNX_THREADS_DEV=100
ONNX_THREADS_CUDA=100
ONNX_THREADS_PROD=100

# в”Җв”Җ WebRTC Engine в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
# mediamtx (default) | mediasoup (stub) | werift (stub)
WEBRTC_ENGINE=mediamtx

# в”Җв”Җ RTSP Capture Backend в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
# Selects the capture engine used to ingest RTSP camera frames for the AI pipeline.
#
# ingest-daemon (default) вҖ” External Python PyAV daemon (ingest_daemon.py, :7070).
#                       The daemon pulls from MediaMTX RTSP loopback
#                       (rtsp://127.0.0.1:MEDIAMTX_RTSP_PORT/{cameraId}) and
#                       POSTs JPEG frames to Node.js via HTTP.
#                       MediaMTX holds ONE connection to the camera; WebRTC (WHEP)
#                       and AI frames share it without a second RTSP pull.
#                       Requires: MediaMTX running + ingest_daemon.py
#                       Config: INGEST_DAEMON_BIN, INGEST_DAEMON_ADDR, INGEST_DAEMON_URL
# mediamtx            вҖ” Polls MediaMTX snapshot REST API for JPEG frames.
#                       GET /v3/paths/{id}/get-snapshot вҶ’ JPEG. No subprocess.
#                       Requires MediaMTX вүҘ 1.2.0 with api: yes in mediamtx.yml.
# ffmpeg              вҖ” FFmpeg subprocess. Widest codec/OS compatibility.
#                       Requires: ffmpeg вүҘ 3.4
# gstreamer           вҖ” GStreamer pipeline. Lower latency; supports hardware decode
#                       (NVIDIA nvdec, Intel/AMD VA-API).
#                       Requires: gstreamer1.0-tools gstreamer1.0-plugins-*
# pyav                вҖ” Python PyAV sidecar. Best CUDA utilisation; future path for
#                       Python-side GPU inference. Requires: pip3 install av Pillow
#
CAPTURE_BACKEND=mediamtx

# RTSP re-publish port exposed by MediaMTX (default 8554).
# Only used when CAPTURE_BACKEND=mediamtx.
MEDIAMTX_RTSP_PORT=8554

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ GStreamer hardware acceleration (only used when CAPTURE_BACKEND=gstreamer) ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# auto      : Auto-detect ??tries nvdec first, then vaapi, falls back to software
# nvdec     : Force NVIDIA NVDEC hardware decode (requires gstreamer1.0-plugins-bad + CUDA)
# vaapi     : Force Intel/AMD VA-API hardware decode (requires gstreamer1.0-vaapi)
# software  : Software decode only (avdec_h264 / decodebin)
GSTREAMER_HW_ACCEL=auto

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ PyAV sidecar (only used when CAPTURE_BACKEND=pyav) ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# Path to the Python interpreter that has PyAV and Pillow installed.
# Priority order:
#   1) PYAV_PYTHON_BIN
#   2) PYAV_PYTHON_BIN_WINDOWS / PYAV_PYTHON_BIN_LINUX (by SERVER_RUNTIME_OS)
#   3) PYTHON_EXEC / PYTHON_EXEC_WINDOWS / PYTHON_EXEC_LINUX
PYAV_PYTHON_BIN=
PYAV_PYTHON_BIN_WINDOWS=C:\Users\young.ho.kim\AppData\Local\Programs\Python\Python312\python.exe
PYAV_PYTHON_BIN_LINUX=/usr/bin/python3
# Hardware accelerator for PyAV decode: none | cuda | vaapi | videotoolbox
PYAV_HW_ACCEL=none

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ RTSP Camera Defaults ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# Default credentials used when auto-discovering ONVIF cameras that have not been
# individually configured. Override per-camera via the REST API or the dashboard.
RTSP_DEFAULT_USERNAME=admin
RTSP_DEFAULT_PASSWORD=

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ AI Model & Inference ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# Path to the YOLOv8 ONNX model file (relative to the server/ directory).
YOLO_MODEL=models/yolov8n.onnx

# Minimum confidence score [0, 1] for a detection to be retained after NMS.
# Lower values increase recall but also false positives.
CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD=0.25

# IoU threshold [0, 1] for Non-Maximum Suppression.
# Overlapping boxes with IoU > this value are merged/suppressed.
NMS_IOU_THRESHOLD=0.5

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ Loitering Detection Parameters ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# Seconds a tracked object must remain in a MONITOR zone before being flagged as loitering.
LOITERING_THRESHOLD_SEC=30

# Minimum pixel displacement between frames to consider an object "moving".
# Objects below this threshold are treated as stationary for dwell-time counting.
MIN_DISPLACEMENT_PX=50

# Seconds within which a re-entering object is linked to the same prior track
# instead of being assigned a new ID.
REENTRY_WINDOW_SEC=120

# Frames without a detection match before a track is considered lost and removed.
MAX_TRACK_AGE_FRAMES=30

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ Security ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# Secret used to sign JWT tokens for API authentication.
# MUST be changed to a long random string in production (e.g. openssl rand -hex 32).
JWT_SECRET=change-me-in-production

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ User Auth (local email + password) ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# JWT RS256 key pair path (relative to server/ directory).
JWT_PRIVATE_KEY_PATH=./certs/jwt.key
JWT_PUBLIC_KEY_PATH=./certs/jwt.pub

# Access/refresh token expiry.
JWT_ACCESS_EXPIRES=15m
JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRES=7d

# Cookie signing secret (32+ byte random hex string).
COOKIE_SECRET=change-me-in-production

# CORS allowed origins for credentialed requests (comma-separated).
CLIENT_ORIGIN=

# First sign-in with this email (local or OAuth) is automatically granted admin.
ADMIN_SEED_EMAIL=

# Auth feature flag - set false to disable auth and allow all API access.
AUTH_ENABLED=true

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ Alert Notifications ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# Webhook URL to POST a JSON payload when a loitering alert fires (leave empty to disable).
ALERT_WEBHOOK_URL=

# E-mail address to send alert notifications to (leave empty to disable e-mail alerts).
ALERT_EMAIL_TO=

# SMTP server settings (required only when ALERT_EMAIL_TO is set).
SMTP_HOST=
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=
SMTP_PASS=

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ File Storage ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# Directory where lts.json, snapshots, and face images are persisted.
# Must be writable by the Node.js process.
STORAGE_PATH=./storage

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ Detection Snapshot Storage ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# SNAPSHOT_ENABLED=false  : Disable all snapshot saving (no I/O overhead)
# SNAPSHOT_INTERVAL_SEC   : Min seconds between periodic snapshots per track
# SNAPSHOT_MAX_PER_CAMERA_DAY : Prune threshold per camera per 24h
# SNAPSHOT_JPEG_QUALITY   : JPEG compression quality 1-100
# SNAPSHOT_MAX_DIMENSION  : Max crop width/height in pixels
SNAPSHOT_ENABLED=true
SNAPSHOT_INTERVAL_SEC=30
SNAPSHOT_MAX_PER_CAMERA_DAY=500
SNAPSHOT_JPEG_QUALITY=70
SNAPSHOT_MAX_DIMENSION=320

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ FFmpeg / Pipeline Limits ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# Maximum number of concurrent camera pipelines (RTSPCapture ffmpeg processes).
# Each active camera = 1 ffmpeg process for frame extraction (10 FPS ??JPEG).
# YouTube streams add 1 additional ffmpeg (yt-dlp ??RTSP) + yt-dlp itself.
# Rule of thumb: 1 pipeline ??1?? CPU cores at 1080p. Set 0 for unlimited.
MAX_PIPELINES=5

# Frames per second extracted by ffmpeg from each RTSP stream for the AI pipeline.
# Lower values reduce CPU/GPU load; higher values improve detection responsiveness.
# Recommended range: 5вҖ“15. Default: 10.
CAPTURE_FPS=15

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ YouTube Stream Limits ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# yt-dlp binary path (auto-detected if empty; set explicitly if not in PATH)
# Use YTDLP_BIN for a single path, or OS-specific overrides below.
YTDLP_BIN=
YTDLP_BIN_WINDOWS=C:\Users\young.ho.kim\AppData\Local\Microsoft\WinGet\Links\yt-dlp.exe
YTDLP_BIN_LINUX=yt-dlp

# MediaMTX binary path (auto-detected if empty; set explicitly if not in PATH).
# Used by devServer.js to auto-start MediaMTX alongside the Node.js server.
MEDIAMTX_BIN=
MEDIAMTX_BIN_WINDOWS=mediamtx
MEDIAMTX_BIN_LINUX=mediamtx

# в”Җв”Җ Ingest Daemon н”„л Ҳмһ„ м ңм–ҙ в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
# analysis лӘЁл“ңм—җм„ңлҠ” ingest-daemonмқҙ мӢӨн–үлҗҳм§Җ м•ҠмңјлҜҖлЎң м•„лһҳ м„Өм •мқҖ м Ғмҡ©лҗҳм§Җ м•ҠмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.
# combined лӘЁл“ң м „нҷҳ мӢң лҳҗлҠ” streaming м„ңлІ„ мёЎ .envм—җм„ң мӮ¬мҡ©н•ҳм„ёмҡ”.
# AI_FRAME_INTERVAL  : AI м„ңлІ„лЎң ліҙлӮј н”„л Ҳмһ„ к°„кІ© (NлІҲм§ё decoded н”„л Ҳмһ„л§ҲлӢӨ м „мҶЎ).  кё°ліёк°’: 3
AI_FRAME_INTERVAL=3
# JPEG_QUALITY : ingest-daemonмқҙ AI м„ңлІ„лЎң ліҙлӮҙлҠ” JPEG м••м¶• н’Ҳм§Ҳ (1-95).  кё°ліёк°’: 85
JPEG_QUALITY=85
# AI_MAX_WIDTH : AI мһ…л Ҙ JPEG мөңлҢҖ к°ҖлЎң н”Ҫм…Җ.  кё°ліёк°’: 640
AI_MAX_WIDTH=640

# Maximum number of simultaneous YouTube-sourced RTSP streams.
# Each stream spawns a yt-dlp process + 1 ffmpeg (mergeвҶ’RTSP); counted separately from MAX_PIPELINES.
YOUTUBE_MAX_STREAMS=2

# Maximum automatic restart attempts per YouTube stream before it is marked as 'error'.
# After this limit the stream must be restarted manually from the dashboard.
YOUTUBE_MAX_RESTARTS=5

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ WebRTC ICE Configuration ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# IP address announced to browsers as the mediasoup SFU host candidate.
# Set to the server's LAN IP that is reachable by the browser's subnet.
# Example: 192.168.1.10
SERVER_IP=

# Optional second announced IP (e.g., a public/external IP).
# Adds an additional host candidate so browsers outside the LAN can also connect.
# Leave empty if the server is not exposed to the public internet.
SERVER_PUBLIC_IP=

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ STUN servers ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# Comma-separated list of STUN URIs.
# Used by the browser to discover its reflexive (NAT-translated) IP address.
# Google's public STUN servers are provided as a fallback; add your own for production.
STUN_URLS=

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ TURN server 1 (LAN / primary) ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# Relay server for browsers that cannot reach the SFU directly (e.g., symmetric NAT).
# Set to a coturn instance on the same subnet as SERVER_IP.
# Leave empty to disable TURN (WebRTC may fail for some clients behind strict NAT).
TURN_URL=
TURN_USERNAME=
TURN_CREDENTIAL=

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ TURN server 2 (public / secondary) ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# Optional second TURN server for clients accessing from outside the LAN.
# Typically points to the same coturn instance via its public IP (SERVER_PUBLIC_IP).
TURN_URL_2=
TURN_USERNAME_2=
TURN_CREDENTIAL_2=

# ?ВҖ?ВҖ OAuth 2.0 ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ?ВҖ
# Base URL of THIS server, used to build callback URLs.
# Example: https://localhost:3443
OAUTH_CALLBACK_BASE=

# Google OAuth 2.0
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=

# Microsoft Entra ID (Azure AD)
MICROSOFT_CLIENT_ID=
MICROSOFT_CLIENT_SECRET=
MICROSOFT_TENANT_ID=common

# Session secret (OAuth state cookie signing).
SESSION_SECRET=change-me-in-production
FFMPEG_BIN_DIR_WINDOWS=C:\Users\young.ho.kim\AppData\Local\Microsoft\WinGet\Links
